item.title: CVE-2020-6213|2024-08-04T08:55:22.059Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20netweaver%20as%20abap%20%28business%20server%20pages%20test%20application%20sbspext_phtmlb%29
item.description: SAP NetWeaver AS ABAP Business Server Pages Test Application SBSPEXT_PHTMLB, versions 700, 701, 702, 730, 731, 740, 750, 751, 752, 753, 754, is vulnerable to reflected Cross-Site Scripting (XSS) via different URL parameters as it does not sufficiently encode user controlled inputs.
